<h1><strong>Ispick Beta</strong></h1>
<p>
  Ispick is an automated anime artworks aggregation service!<br />
You can create various anime image feeds based on text tags.<br />
This is the beta version, so your favorites and followed tags data could be deleted.
</p>

<div class="top-image">
  <%= link_to (image_tag asset_path('top_madoka.jpg')), '/', style: " z-index: 1;"%>
</div>

<div class="wrapper-oauth">
  <div class="btn-group-vertical btn-group-oauth">
    <%= bs_button_to 'Continue with Facebook', user_omniauth_authorize_path(:facebook), class: "btn btn-default btn-block" %><br>
    <%= bs_button_to 'Continue with Twitter', user_omniauth_authorize_path(:twitter), class: "btn btn-default btn-block" %><br>
    <%= bs_button_to 'Continue with Tumblr',  user_omniauth_authorize_path(:tumblr), class: "btn btn-default btn-block" %><br>
    <%= bs_button_to 'Continue with Email', '/sign_up', class: "btn btn-default btn-block" %><br>
  </div>
  <div align="center">
    <%= bs_button_to 'Login', '/signin_with_password', class: 'btn-mini btn-default' %>
  </div>
</div>
